{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Cookie","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Glossary/Cookie","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Una cookie es una pequeña información enviada por un sitio web que se almacena&nbsp;en el navegador&nbsp;del ordenador del usuario.</p>\n\n<p>Las cookies sirven para personalizar la experiencia que tiene el&nbsp;usuario al navegar por&nbsp;un sitio web.&nbsp;Pueden contener las preferencias del usuario o entradas de información al acceder a dicha web.&nbsp;El usuario puede personalizar su navegador para aceptar, rechazar, o borrar&nbsp;las cookies.</p>\n\n<p>Las cookies pueden establecerse y modificarse desde el lado del servidor mediante el&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Cookies\">encabezado&nbsp;HTTP</a>&nbsp;<code>Set-Cookie</code>&nbsp;o usando&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/cookie\">document.cookie</a></code>&nbsp;en JavaScript.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"saber_más","title":"Saber más","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conocimiento_general","title":"Conocimiento general","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cookie_(inform%C3%A1tica)\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Cookie</a>&nbsp;en Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Saber más","id":"saber_más"}],"summary":"Una cookie es una pequeña información enviada por un sitio web que se almacena en el navegador del ordenador del usuario.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Cookie","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/glossary/cookie","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/glossary/cookie/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Glossary","title":"Glosario"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Glossary/Cookie","title":"Cookie"}],"pageTitle":"Cookie - Glosario | MDN","noIndexing":false}}